# ─── DeepFace / AI Models ───────────────────────────────────
# Model weights are large — download on first run
.deepface/
*.h5
*.pkl
*.pt
*.pth

# Every uploaded/captured file (employee reference photos + AI model cache,
# audit photos, HR documents — sensitive personal data / runtime data) lives
# under this one root now instead of separate top-level folders (see
# AGENTS.md's Unified Uploads Root rule). Anchored to repo root — an
# unanchored `uploads/` could in principle match a future frontend folder of
# the same name; verify with `git status --ignored` after touching this line.
/uploads/

